description: Himeko is the violent "yankee"-girl with a soft spot for cute things. She is the fighter/ brawn to the Sket-Dan. In her past she was called "Legendary Yankee Onihime" which became a symbol of "power and fear". Himeko seems to now have "calmed down" from her days of being the Onihime and has become the second-chief to the Sket-Dan.
name: Himeko
